<plot>Six soldier; six different time periods and one letter unites them. Our nation's history is reflected in the one fundamental value of every American soldier during times of war - the passion to write a letter home. No matter who the enemy was or what consequences are at stake, it was an American letter that defined them as American Soldiers.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?036616</url></doc>
